[SN]TITLE[SN]
New appeal over 'dangerous' ex-prisoner Martin Hamilton

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Police have renewed their appeal for help in finding a potentially dangerous ex-prisoner.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Martin Hamilton was released from prison on licence in September 2014 and is now wanted in relation to a Revocation of Licence Warrant.
The 53-year-old is described as white and has short cropped fair hair.
Police Scotland said Hamilton may be dangerous and urged members of the public not to approach him and to contact officers if they saw him.
